Class Bale

java.lang.Object
  exploris.motion.MobileObject
      exploris.aquarium.Turtle
          Turtle
              Bale

public class Bale
extends Turtle

Did you know that one of the collective nouns for turtles is "bale"? This class allows you to represent a bale. Turtles in a bale can be instructed as one.
